Jon Rubinstein

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

For the actor, see John Rubinstein.


Jon Rubinstein



Rubinstein (l) with HP executive Todd Bradley, presenting webOS phones in 2011.



Born
Jonathan J. Rubinstein
October 1956 (age 60)
New York City, New York


Alma mater
Cornell University
Colorado State University


Known for
Playing key role in development of Apple's iPod and iMac, and webOS


